5.Cache support.
6.Primary Key generated support.
7.Data validation support in form of Annotation(JSR0003).(irrspective of presentation and controller validation)
8.Exception Free(Run time).
9.Object Graph Mapping.OGM support(NOSql database or Hadup base database).
10.Indext based searching support.
11.Connecton pool implementations.

